1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 18=

11
00:01:23,079 --> 00:01:23,879
How is she?

12
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,799
Based on her pulse,

13
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:28,519
prolonging her life

14
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,200
has triggered the curse.

15
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:32,120
Her blood is flowing backward.

16
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,000
This curse

17
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:35,959
is now accelerating the extraction

18
00:01:35,959 --> 00:01:38,359
of her life essence.

19
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:39,719
What do we do?

20
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,040
Well...

21
00:01:42,959 --> 00:01:44,200
Find a way!

22
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,400
No matter the cost,

23
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,120
you must bring her back!

24
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,959
There is one way.

25
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,359
But...

26
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:55,519
It requires the union
of male and female energies,

27
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:58,400
yin and yang in perfect balance,

28
00:01:58,959 --> 00:02:00,599
to channel spiritual power into her.

29
00:02:08,319 --> 00:02:09,520
I'll step out first.

30
00:02:10,319 --> 00:02:11,759
You two talk it out.

31
00:02:25,879 --> 00:02:28,280
(If I could transfer the curse
onto myself,)

32
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:30,800
(would Ningxue be safe?)

33
00:02:55,319 --> 00:02:56,120
Su Wubing.

34
00:02:56,719 --> 00:02:57,479
Are you alright?

35
00:02:59,000 --> 00:02:59,800
I'm fine.

36
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:22,800
What are you doing?

37
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:27,800
I heard everything Mr. Ye said.

38
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:29,960
Listen carefully.

39
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,000
Neither of us

40
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,120
is allowed to die.

41
00:04:41,439 --> 00:04:43,560
Master, is this...?

42
00:04:49,199 --> 00:04:50,519
As expected,

43
00:04:51,439 --> 00:04:52,600
his body is terrifyingly strong.

44
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:58,959
You already sensed me?

45
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:07,160
After last night,
the pain seems a bit better.

46
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:09,079
But is the curse still there?

47
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,879
The power I infused into you

48
00:06:10,959 --> 00:06:12,199
can suppress it for now.

49
00:06:12,639 --> 00:06:13,800
But when the time comes...

50
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:15,079
I believe you.

51
00:06:16,759 --> 00:06:17,319
Ningxue.

52
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:45,480
So this is why grandpa
didn't want me coming here.

53
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,600
The two of you are together.

54
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,079
(So it is her.)

55
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,519
Su Wubing.

56
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:13,319
You promised me you'd cure my illness.

57
00:07:17,399 --> 00:07:17,959
Illness?

58
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,800
What illness can't Mr. Ye cure?

59
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,160
My illness?

60
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:25,639
Only Su Wubing can help with that.

61
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:27,839
Don't forget...

62
00:07:27,839 --> 00:07:28,759
What kind of illness is it?

63
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:29,279
So mysterious.

64
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:32,319
Of course it's...

65
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,120
(After refining the final Cold Marrow,)

66
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:08,399
(I'm only one step away
from the Heavenly God Realm.)

67
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:10,759
Xiaonuan.

68
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,759
The Cold Marrow in your body

69
00:08:13,399 --> 00:08:14,720
is almost fully refined.

70
00:08:15,839 --> 00:08:19,000
The rest can be treated
by your grandfather.

71
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:23,759
Are you already with Lin Ningxue?

72
00:08:33,399 --> 00:08:34,200
Answer me.

73
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,000
Look at me.

74
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:42,200
I just want to know

75
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:45,360
was there ever a place for me
in your heart?

76
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:47,720
Even for a moment?

77
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:52,919
Xiaonuan.

78
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,960
Ningxue and I are destined.

79
00:08:56,879 --> 00:08:59,360
We can't be separated.

80
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:03,440
I didn't like you
just because you cured me.

81
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:03,960
I...

82
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:04,720
I know.

83
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:07,120
But my heart belongs only to her.

84
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,919
Am I really not good enough?

85
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:36,120
Mr. Gu, ever since the tournament,

86
00:09:36,919 --> 00:09:40,120
all major families in Fan City
have started backing the Lin family.

87
00:09:40,759 --> 00:09:42,399
Our stock price...

88
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,360
it's collapsing.

89
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:47,120
What did you say?

90
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,879
And the reclusive Fang family

91
00:09:52,519 --> 00:09:54,799
seems to be supporting them
from behind as well.

92
00:09:56,039 --> 00:09:58,360
If we still want to take over
the Lin Group,

93
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,759
we might have to...

94
00:10:02,919 --> 00:10:03,720
Say it.

95
00:10:05,679 --> 00:10:07,120
We might have to

96
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:10,000
make peace with the Lin family.

97
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,360
Seek their help.

98
00:10:13,919 --> 00:10:15,960
What? Get out!

99
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:24,279
Mr. Gu, why are you so angry?

100
00:10:24,759 --> 00:10:26,919
The Gu family has vast resources.

101
00:10:26,919 --> 00:10:28,759
Why fear a comeback from the Lin family?

102
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:32,360
If I had known this would happen,

103
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:34,080
I should've killed Su Wubing

104
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,080
before the tournament.

105
00:10:41,519 --> 00:10:42,440
Mr. Gu.

106
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:47,720
I've stayed by your side for so long,

107
00:10:47,919 --> 00:10:49,559
loyal and devoted.

108
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:51,759
So...?

109
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,360
What do you want?

110
00:10:57,639 --> 00:10:59,440
That depends on what you can give me.

111
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:03,679
If I become Mrs. Gu...

112
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:05,000
that would be...

113
00:11:08,519 --> 00:11:09,320
How about this.

114
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:12,080
From now on, you'll manage
the entire Gu Group.

115
00:11:12,519 --> 00:11:13,320
How's that?

116
00:11:14,039 --> 00:11:14,879
Really?

117
00:11:19,799 --> 00:11:22,080
Here's a slap to wake you up.

118
00:11:22,279 --> 00:11:23,720
Mrs. Gu?

119
00:11:23,879 --> 00:11:25,320
Look at yourself.

120
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,399
You dare hit back?

121
00:11:56,326 --> 00:12:00,429
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

122
00:12:00,429 --> 00:12:05,149
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

123
00:12:05,149 --> 00:12:10,029
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

124
00:12:10,029 --> 00:12:15,149
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

125
00:12:15,149 --> 00:12:19,549
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

126
00:12:19,549 --> 00:12:24,229
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

127
00:12:24,229 --> 00:12:29,629
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

128
00:12:29,629 --> 00:12:36,023
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪
